name: Sol Strikers
description:
Score the most points in the time limit to win the round! Best 2 out of 3!

Player 1- Quetzaud-Green: Controls are A,D to move;  W to jump - cant float temporarily in mid air with jump

Player 2- Catalinia - Purple: J, L to move 'i' to jump - can double jump
